text: Kireedamillatha Rajakkanmar () is a 1996 Indian Malayalam-language film directed by Kalabhavan Ansar and starring Jagadish, Prem Kumar, Jagathy Sreekumar and Annie. ==Plot== ==Cast== * Jagadish as Maruti Shankar * Prem Kumar as Tender Sarasan * Jagathy Sreekumar as Pushpul Raghavan * Kalabhavan Mani as Superfast Chandran * Abi as Meter Koya, Amina Ithaatha * Narayanankutty as Thekkan Pathrose * Annie as Bincy (James Bond Nancy), Nancy * Innocent as Bharathan * Philomina as Sarkar Saramma * Silk Smitha as Rajamma * Saikumar as Mathews * Jagannatha Varma as Carlton Nicholas * Dharsana as Seetha, Bharathan's daughter * Augustine as SI Kozhi Vasu * Thesni Khan as Rexi * Mini Arun as Sheela * Ponnamma Babu as Hostel warden ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 films Category:Indian films Category:1990s Malayalam-language films Category:Indian comedy films
title: Kireedamillatha Rajakkanmar
